ty dollars. These other coins are more fully described in Coins of the United States dollar. The...', DEFAULT, 'Books LLC, Wiki Series', DEFAULT, 'Currencies of Oceania: Australian Dollar, New Zealand Dollar, Indonesian Rupiah, CFP Franc, United States Dollar, Pound Sterling in Australia', '2010-09');
